Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.27,0:00:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE]\NThis guy's name is Bojji.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.06,0:00:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,He can't talk and he can't hear,\Nand to make matters worse,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.48,0:00:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,he's too naïve and kindhearted\Nfor his own good.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.73,0:00:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But his fancy clothes caught my\Nattention, and before I knew it,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.28,0:00:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd followed him straight into\Nthe predicament I'm in now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.32,0:00:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,As if society hadn't thrown\Nenough grief my way,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.45,0:00:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,someone in town figured out I\Nwas a member of the Shadow Clan,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.62,0:00:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,who used to work\Nas killers for hire.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.79,0:00:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,If only I'd done the smart\Nthing and run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.54,0:00:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But then I heard that Bojji\Nwould be sparring with
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.79,0:00:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,his younger brother Daida, who's\Nalready a skilled swordsman.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.30,0:00:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And for some reason, I decided\Nto stick around and watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.23,0:02:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.24,0:02:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,[SHADOW CLAN whimpering]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.08,0:02:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,[screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.71,0:02:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.84,0:02:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE'S MOTHER gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.67,0:02:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hide!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.80,0:02:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't hide forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.47,0:02:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.89,0:02:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE'S MOTHER] There's someone\Nfrom the Light Clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.35,0:02:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Kage, I need you to keep\Nrunning by yourself, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.31,0:02:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE gasps]\NWhat about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.19,0:03:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mom shouldn't have\Nany trouble with these men,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.15,0:03:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,but I can't fight them unless I\Nknow you're out of harm's way,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.65,0:03:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,so you have to keep running.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.99,0:03:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll catch up with you\Nin the toxic forest up ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.82,0:03:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.99,0:03:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE whimpers]\NMm...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.95,0:03:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE'S MOTHER] You are so\Nprecious to me, my sweet Kage.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.20,0:03:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.00,0:03:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE'S MOTHER]\NRight. Now go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.58,0:03:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.79,0:03:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE]\NHurry, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.92,0:03:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE'S MOTHER]\NI'll crush them!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.92,0:03:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,White light!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.22,0:03:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE'S MOTHER gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.43,0:03:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Found you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.59,0:03:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,One of them got away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.97,0:03:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.89,0:03:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE'S MOTHER]\NNo, you don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.47,0:03:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Your kind are powerful\Nin the shadows,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.98,0:03:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,but quite weak once exposed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.40,0:03:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Rather bold of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.90,0:03:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE'S MOTHER] Geslan,\Nwhat poison have you whispered
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.69,0:03:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,in the king's ear?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.32,0:03:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I hardly see any call\Nfor such accusations.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.70,0:03:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a look, my dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.08,0:03:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I can offer a painless death,\Nso save us the trouble
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.21,0:03:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and keep still.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.04,0:04:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.21,0:04:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's the toxic forest...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.50,0:04:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Still that far?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.76,0:04:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.34,0:04:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE]\NM-Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.43,0:04:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.94,0:04:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,[GESLAN] Goodness,\Nbut you're a stubborn one!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.19,0:04:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE'S MOTHER]\NI hope you escaped, Kage...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.90,0:04:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama won't be catching up...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.11,0:04:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,[GESLAN] I suppose you\Nwere trying to buy time for
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.90,0:04:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,that brat of yours, but I\Nbelieve it was already captured
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.32,0:04:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,by another patrol.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.53,0:04:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE'S MOTHER shrieks]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.95,0:04:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,[slashing]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.72,0:04:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[KNIGHT 2A] My, if it isn't\Nthe young countess, Poise.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.63,0:04:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Did a shadow clan child\Njust pass by here, miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.97,0:04:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,[KNIGHT 2A]\NWhat a creepy little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.02,0:05:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Fled to the forest, as expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.35,0:05:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You have our thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.36,0:05:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[GESLAN]\NDid you finish it yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.99,0:05:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,[KNIGHT 2A]\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.36,0:05:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It appears to have fled\Ninto the toxic forest, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.28,0:05:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,[GESLAN growls]\NGet after it, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.62,0:05:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,[HORSE whinnies]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.58,0:05:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE gasps]\NMama..!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.00,0:05:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- [shrieks]\N- [POISE gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.88,0:05:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,- [shrieking continues]\N- [POISE wails]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.80,0:05:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[SERVANT 2A gasps]\NWhat could be the matter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.47,0:05:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, be on your way, sirs!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.34,0:05:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You're frightening\Nthe young lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.81,0:05:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[KNIGHT 2A]\NWe beg your pardon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.68,0:05:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Geslan, let us go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.60,0:05:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,- [GESLAN] Tch!\N- [wailing continues]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.48,0:05:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE wailing]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.87,0:05:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,As servants of King Bo,\Nwe offer our aid,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.62,0:05:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,though this is all\Nwe have to give.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.83,0:06:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll reach another kingdom\Nfurther down this path.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.71,0:06:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,There, you will find safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.79,0:06:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE whimpers]\NThank you very much...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.13,0:06:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.38,0:06:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[POISE]\NDo you think he'll be all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.68,0:06:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Although the Shadow Clan\Nis fallen,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.68,0:06:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,their strength is sure\Nto see him through.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.97,0:06:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, we must be on\Nour way too, I'm afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.04,0:06:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE whimpering]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.51,0:06:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[stomach growling]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.39,0:06:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,[stomach growling continues]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.97,0:07:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE whimpering]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.40,0:07:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,- [stomach growling]\N- [KAGE groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.91,0:07:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE'S MOTHER] Here, Kage! I\Nhave a birthday present for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.16,0:07:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE]\NReally?! Oh, boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.16,0:07:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.75,0:07:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- Thank you, Mama!\N- [KAGE'S MOTHER chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.00,0:07:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.38,0:07:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE] Can I trade you\Nthis for an apple...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.63,0:07:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,If you wanna buy\Nsomething, bring money!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.68,0:07:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,[TOWNSWOMAN 2A]\NI'll take four of these, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.01,0:07:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.94,0:07:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,[TOWNSWOMAN 2B gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.40,0:07:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Get back here right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.81,0:07:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.07,0:07:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.40,0:07:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,[whines]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.24,0:07:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,[blows thudding]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.75,0:08:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.60,0:08:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,[TOWNSMAN 2A]\NHmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.64,0:08:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE whimpering]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.53,0:08:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you lookin' at?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.91,0:08:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I give you food,\NI expect you to eat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.20,0:08:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You got a problem with that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.00,0:08:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE whimpers]\NNo, sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.25,0:08:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[TOWNSMAN 2A]\NCome to think of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.79,0:08:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I might just need you to\Nstart bringin' in some coin
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.21,0:08:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,for my trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.76,0:09:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Get inside here and\Nopen the door for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.35,0:09:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.73,0:09:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE]\NMm. Yes, sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.23,0:09:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Nicely done.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.16,0:09:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.16,0:09:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.41,0:09:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.41,0:09:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You pulled it off, shadow buddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.29,0:09:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.05,0:09:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,[TOWNSMAN 2A]\NThere we go...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.55,0:09:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Good work, bud.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.68,0:09:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Your cut.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.18,0:09:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.35,0:09:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.86,0:09:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,[snoring]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.74,0:10:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.58,0:10:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,[TOWNSMAN 2A] Damn it,\Nhow could I have lost again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.25,0:10:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't stand for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.62,0:10:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]\NAh―
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.54,0:10:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.30,0:10:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.34,0:10:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.67,0:10:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.43,0:10:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE snoring softly]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.43,0:10:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE] Mama, you and\Nthe others are some kinda
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.52,0:10:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,super powerful\Nassassins, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.68,0:10:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So tell me about all the scary\Nbad guys you've gotten rid of!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.85,0:10:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE'S MOTHER]\NLet's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.48,0:10:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We kill whoever we're\Nordered to, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.94,0:10:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Women, children,\Nthe old and infirm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.53,0:10:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE]\NUh! You're joking!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.65,0:10:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE'S MOTHER]\NIt's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.24,0:10:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why we couldn't object\Nif someone were to try and kill
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.53,0:10:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,all of us, down the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.49,0:10:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE]\NBut why do you do that stuff...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.45,0:10:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE'S MOTHER] Hmm... Perhaps\Nit's these bodies of ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.71,0:10:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,They're perfectly suited\Nto doing awful things.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.63,0:11:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE'S MOTHER] But listen...\NWe do everything we can
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.13,0:11:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,in order to serve the interests\Nof the people who need us most,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.01,0:11:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and that is the light\Nthat guides us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.68,0:11:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE'S MOTHER gasps]\NOh no! They're coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.02,0:11:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,- Wake up, Kage!\N- [footsteps approaching]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.35,0:11:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE grunts, gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.37,0:11:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[SOLDIER 2A gasps]\NThere!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.37,0:11:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It just slipped out the window!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.58,0:11:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,After it! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.92,0:11:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[TOWNSMAN 2A chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.47,0:11:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,[SOLDIER 2B] It's gone.\NWe'll never find it in the dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.34,0:11:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[TOWNSMAN 2A snoring]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.89,0:11:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,[knocking]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.18,0:11:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's here knockin'\Nat this hour?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.52,0:11:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.14,0:11:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You? What are you\Ndoing back here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.77,0:12:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.86,0:12:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm done with you!\NGet lost already!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.19,0:12:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoo! Scat!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.91,0:12:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE whines]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.33,0:12:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,[PATRONS chattering]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.25,0:12:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[TOWNSMAN 2A gulping]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.71,0:12:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[TOWNSMAN 2B grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.01,0:12:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.55,0:12:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[yelps]\NPlease, don't hurt me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.85,0:12:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,[TOWNSMAN 2A] You should watch\Nwhat you're doing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.10,0:12:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,- [blows thudding]\N- [TOWNSMAN 2B grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.48,0:12:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- [slice]\N- [TOWNSMAN 2A yelps]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.48,0:12:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,[TOWNSMAN 2A whimpering]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.61,0:12:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,[groaning]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.86,0:12:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.94,0:12:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's not a\Npitiful way to go...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.83,0:12:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE whimpering]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.92,0:13:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[TOWNSMAN 2A sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.67,0:13:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE gasps, whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.17,0:13:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,[PATRONS murmuring]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.55,0:13:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,- [TOWNSMAN 2E] Get outta here!\N- [KAGE gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.89,0:13:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,[TOWNSMEN grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.73,0:13:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE whimpering]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.48,0:14:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE chuckles]\NScored big today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.11,0:14:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,This haul oughta keep me\Nfed for a good long while.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.65,0:14:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Who the heck are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.82,0:14:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, get back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.66,0:14:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOJJI]\NAh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.99,0:14:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't seen you\Naround here before.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.99,0:14:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE] Why did I put myself\Nin danger just to come back
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.29,0:14:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,for this little runt?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.58,0:14:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,[DOMAS]\NBegin!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.96,0:14:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.04,0:14:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.38,0:14:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,- [KAGE gasps]\N- Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.26,0:14:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.30,0:14:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE gasps]\NAh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.30,0:14:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[DAIDA grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.59,0:14:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.89,0:14:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOJJI]\NAu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.81,0:14:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE]\NYou're not bad at all, Bojji!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.94,0:14:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,[DOMAS] I never realized\NPrince Bojji was so capable!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.86,0:14:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,[DOMAS]\NBut now...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.37,0:14:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,[DAIDA growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.29,0:15:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.33,0:15:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.16,0:15:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.33,0:15:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.54,0:15:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,[growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.46,0:15:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.47,0:15:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE]\NYes, Bojji!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.63,0:15:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You can tell what people\Nare saying just by
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.22,0:15:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,watching their lips!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.55,0:15:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Your eyes and\Nyour insight are sharp!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.85,0:15:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince Daida appears on\Nthe verge of defeat,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.15,0:15:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,just what do you make of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.90,0:15:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You think he's losing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.56,0:15:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,He clearly seems\Nunable to defend himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.98,0:15:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughs] Prince Bojji lacks\Nthe strength to land
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.70,0:15:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,a decisive blow, and if,\Nby some miracle, he should win,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.70,0:15:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,it will prove him\Nunworthy of the crown.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.24,0:15:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,[SOLDIER 2C] Say, doesn't\NPrince Bojji's way of fighting
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.33,0:15:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,seem a bit dirty?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.00,0:15:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[SOLDIER 2D]\NTrue. Cowardly, even.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.46,0:15:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,[SOLDIER 2E]\NUnderhanded.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.58,0:15:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[SOLDIER 2F]\NIt disgusts me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.92,0:15:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[SOLDIER 2G]\NHe's a sneak.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.46,0:15:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE]\NThat's it! You got it, Bojji!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.42,0:15:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[BEBIN] To the those watching,\NIt seems he's making sport
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.59,0:15:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,of his opponent's\Ndesperate efforts,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.30,0:15:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,and that's turning\Nthem against him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.43,0:16:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But this kind of trickery\Nis the only way for someone
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.89,0:16:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,so weak to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.97,0:16:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[BEBIN] So what will\Nyou do, Prince Bojji?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.23,0:16:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,[DAIDA growls]\NDamn!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.02,0:16:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You fight dirty, Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.95,0:16:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.49,0:16:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE]\NWhat? What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.54,0:16:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Surely you needn't\Nsay it so coldly, Domas.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.50,0:16:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Either way,\Nit needed to be said.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.09,0:16:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.25,0:16:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOJJI groaning]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.68,0:16:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,- [DAIDA growls]\N- [coughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.35,0:16:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE]\NHey, why'd you quit dodging?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.02,0:16:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- [DAIDA grunting]\N- [BOJJI groaning]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.48,0:16:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,[DAIDA panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.82,0:16:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,[growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.86,0:16:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,- [grunting]\N- [blows cracking]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.24,0:16:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody, stop him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.74,0:16:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,- [grunting continues]\N- [blows thudding]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.82,0:17:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,[DAIDA panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.91,0:17:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOJJI whimpering]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.70,0:17:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE gasps]\NBojji...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.70,0:17:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[SOLDIERS murmuring]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.79,0:17:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,[DAIDA growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.83,0:17:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,- [KAGE whimpering]\N- [DAIDA yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.38,0:17:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[blows thudding]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.80,0:17:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE whimpering]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.14,0:17:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,- Stop...\N- [DAIDA growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.51,0:17:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE]\NStop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.77,0:17:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,[DOMAS]\NHmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.98,0:17:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,[DOMAS]\NApeas...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.23,0:17:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Match over!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.32,0:17:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince Daida has prevailed!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.11,0:17:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone get him a doctor, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.74,0:17:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE gasps]\NBojji...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.46,0:17:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Apeas. I know what\Nyou're trying to tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.71,0:17:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry,\Nbut please understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.21,0:18:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Shame on you for using
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.34,0:18:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,such underhanded\Ntactics, Big Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.68,0:18:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,[DAIDA] Hmph. Now you can\Nnever handle a sword again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.60,0:18:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What exactly did\NDomas say to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.81,0:18:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah. "That is not\Nthe swordsmanship of a king.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.27,0:18:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The two of you\Nmust trade blows."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.32,0:18:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughs] Then everything is\Nplaying out just as predicted.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.11,0:18:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.91,0:18:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,[MAGIC MIRROR]\NWelcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.58,0:18:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. It would seem\Nmy path to the throne
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.37,0:18:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,is clearing up quickly,\Njust as you said it would.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.51,0:18:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOJJI panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.22,0:18:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[DOMAS] He shows great skill at\Nevading his opponent's blows,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.22,0:18:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,but even with a short sword,\Nhe can't strike back decisively,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.68,0:18:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,so he can't defeat his enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.27,0:18:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And he was born under\Na star that won't let him
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.27,0:18:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,grow stronger. I truly pity him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.98,0:19:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall return.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.74,0:19:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE]\NSo that was Domas?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.08,0:19:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I know his type.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.83,0:19:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You can never count\Non guys like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.25,0:19:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.33,0:19:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[SOLDIER 2H]\NThat's dirty swordplay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.17,0:19:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,How cowardly!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.09,0:19:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[DOMAS] "This is not the\Nswordsmanship of a king."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.09,0:19:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOJJI whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.72,0:19:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE]\NHey, where you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.52,0:19:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't get out\Nof bed like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.31,0:19:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOJJI whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.07,0:19:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[sword clanks]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.74,0:19:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.74,0:19:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[groaning]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.37,0:19:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.41,0:19:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE]\NBojji...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.00,0:19:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOJJI whimpering]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.58,0:20:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.80,0:20:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,[sobs softly]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.01,0:20:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,[whimpering]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.15,0:20:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,[sobbing]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.36,0:20:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Au.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.78,0:20:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE] You've got nothing\Nto be embarrassed about.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.82,0:20:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I was watching that match.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.70,0:20:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You won that fight and\Nmade it look easy, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.45,0:20:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold your head up high, kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.54,0:20:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You were doing just fine\Nfighting your own way,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.66,0:20:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,so don't let any of\Nthose fools tell you not to!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.13,0:20:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]\NAu, au!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.84,0:20:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen― I'm not\Ntaking anything else
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.92,0:20:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,from you anymore, got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.01,0:20:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how\Nthis is gonna sound,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.89,0:20:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and I get that\Nit's outta nowhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.35,0:20:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.22,0:20:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I just--!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.48,0:20:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm on your side, all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.39,0:21:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what happens!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.81,0:21:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOJJI gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.28,0:21:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,[whimpering]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.90,0:21:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE]\NAnd I mean what I'm saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.11,0:21:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got your back\Nfrom now on, Bojji.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.87,0:21:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Always.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.07,0:21:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOJJI whimpering]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.25,0:21:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
